This paper deals with physical-layer security in a wireless communication system, which falls under the scope of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also addresses the issue of potential eavesdropping, which is a common concern in the field of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed algorithm involves optimizing the UAV's trajectory, which is a problem commonly studied in the field of robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
